    "3842341": {
      "title": "CNVs conferring risk of autism or schizophrenia affect cognition in controls",
      "abstract": "Rare copy-number variants (CNVs) conferring risk of schizophrenia or autism affect fecundity of carriers in Iceland, and carriers of these CNVs who do not suffer disease or have not been diagnosed with intellectual disability show phenotypes in brain structure and cognitive abilities between those of non-carrier controls and patients with schizophrenia."
